    Package: com.paulmender.udacity.popularmovies.content Project: PopularMovies Stage 2 Name: AsyncTaskBundleWrapper Purpose: Since Bundle cannot be subclassed, wrap it in a class. Also provides standard bundle keys (enum BundleKey) and support for related values. Author: Paul on 20171006. History: 20171127 Refactored copy of com.paulmender.android.os.FetchDataParameters. 20180102 Refactored, a "push down", from MovieDbAsyncTaskBundleWrapper.java. The primary objective was to eliminate application specific references while maintaining class interactions.
